<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    {{> styles}}
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        {{> header}}

        <div class="content">
            <div class="notice-header">3-Day Notice</div>

            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><strong>{{currentDate}}</strong></p>

            <p>
                <strong>{{tenantName}}</strong><br>
                {{#if tenantAddress}}{{tenantAddress}}{{/if}}
            </p>

            <p>Via Email</p>

            <p style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                RE: 3 DAY NOTICE TO PAY OUTSTANDING BALANCE OR DELIVER POSSESSION {{propertyName}}
            </p>

            <p class="greeting">Dear {{firstName}},</p>

            <p>
                Notwithstanding any previous Notices provided, you are hereby notified that, as of the date above, you
                are indebted to the Landlord in the sum of ${{outstandingBalance}} for rent plus late fee of
                ${{lateFee}} through {{monthEnd}}, and use of the Premises, {{premisesAddress}} thru today's date, now
                occupied by you and demand payment of all outstanding balance or possession of the premises within 3
                days (excluding Saturday, Sunday and legal Holidays) From The date of delivery of this notice, to wit on
                or before the <strong>{{expirationDate}}</strong>.
            </p>

            <p style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">
                Total amount owed: ${{totalAmount}}
            </p>

            <p style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px;">
                LANDLORD DOES NOT ACCEPT PARTIAL PAYMENTS
            </p>

            <p>
                PLEASE MAKE ALL CHECKS PAYABLE TO: <strong>{{payTo}}</strong>
            </p>

            <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.</p>

            <div class="closing">
                <p>
                    <strong>{{managerName}}</strong><br>
                    {{managerTitle}}<br>
                    Global Fund Investments
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px dashed #e2e8f0; font-size: 13px;">
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">Contact for Tenant:-</p>
                <p>
                    <strong>{{tenantName}}</strong><br>
                    <strong>{{propertyName}}</strong><br>
                    <strong>{{tenantAddress}}</strong><br>
                    <strong>{{tenantMail}}</strong><br>
                    <strong>{{tenantContact}}</strong>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        {{> footer}}
    </div>
</body>

</html>